snippet.title: Torq's Late (to the Grand Prix in the Attic Upstairs) — AVAILABLE NOW!
snippet.description:
You're Torq, a toy car...
...but more importantly, you're running late!

Using your trusty pullback motor and unlockable upgrades, overcome the treacherous terrain of an unkempt living room!

► Master the temperamental pullback motor!
► Rally your way through a messy living room!
► Collect coins and upgrade yourself at the garage!

PLAY FOR FREE TODAY AT ITCH.IO
https://xenikobalt.itch.io/torq-is-late

This game is a collaborative effort by barkScript, CaveL1ghter, and Xeni. It was completed in four days as part of the 2024 Game Maker's Toolkit Game Jam.

Special thanks to Peachanas for their 150+ Lowpoly Furniture & Decor pack!
